300
00:15:23.219 --> 00:15:27.320
"Is my nephew's name benjamin or Linda?"

301
00:15:28.160 --> 00:15:29.820
"Benjamin."
Correct.

302
00:15:29.850 --> 00:15:31.980
That was an either/or question.

303
00:15:32.010 --> 00:15:34.539
Not a "yes" or "no".
It's a bit more difficult, right?

304
00:15:34.739 --> 00:15:36.460
Because now you can't just
