438
00:22:45.520 --> 00:22:48.140
Okay?
And I don't need to, right?

439
00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:51.860
But you have to realize that there this
is just the first level of fluency.

440
00:22:51.890 --> 00:22:56.140
And so don't have that expectation that,
