441
00:22:56.170 --> 00:23:00.460
to understand every single thing I hear
in English and make very few mistakes.

442
00:23:00.490 --> 00:23:01.940
No, that's not how it works.

443
00:23:01.960 --> 00:23:05.920
You can reach this level, which is a very,
very good level, but that's gonna take you

444
00:23:05.950 --> 00:23:08.362
three to six months with 1 hour a day
