consuming.

447
00:23:14.170 --> 00:23:15.330
And that's fine.

448
00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:17.810
So remember here, be patient.

449
00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:19.090
Languages don't have an end.

450
00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:21.940
To lose patience is
to lose the battle, right?

451
00:23:21.970 --> 00:23:25.620
And then we have complete fluency,
