455
00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:40.460
But don't think about it as that.

456
00:23:40.490 --> 00:23:44.180
Think about it as a process,
like a, a lifetime process.

457
00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:45.090
Think about it like that

458
00:23:45.120 --> 00:23:50.380
even though we have hard goals and we
