459
00:23:50.410 --> 00:23:52.700
But be patient,
languages don't have an end.

460
00:23:52.730 --> 00:23:54.810
Enjoy the process.
Okay?

461
00:23:54.840 --> 00:23:57.620
Rule number eleven,
consistency over intensity.

462
00:23:57.650 --> 00:23:59.570
Consistency over intensity.

463
00:23:59.600 --> 00:24:00.860
Read this quote here.

464
00:24:00.890 --> 00:24:04.810
Imperfect action is better
than perfect inaction.

465
00:24:04.840 --> 00:24:05.900
All right?

466
00:24:05.930 --> 00:24:07.460
It's all about consistency.

467
00:24:07.490 --> 00:24:09.220
And I've said this so many times.

468
00:24:09.250 --> 00:24:11.290
I don't care if you study 5 hours

469
00:24:11.320 --> 00:24:15.220
on a Sunday and then stop
studying on the weekdays.

470
00:24:16.050 --> 00:24:17.653
No, that's terrible!

471
00:24:17.853 --> 00:24:21.420
Consistency.
Every single day you need to study.

472
00:24:21.450 --> 00:24:23.460
You need to advance through the stories,

473
00:24:23.480 --> 00:24:26.940
you need to review your phrases
in the RAIO App, every single day.

474
00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:29.570
I'm not telling you you have
to do it for an hour a day.

475
00:24:29.600 --> 00:24:32.860
I'm not telling you you have to do
it for even 30 minutes a day.

476
00:24:32.890 --> 00:24:36.200
You can do it 15 minutes a day,
minimum 15 minutes a day.

477
00:24:36.230 --> 00:24:38.740
But make sure you do it every single day.
Why?

478
00:24:38.770 --> 00:24:41.020
Because then you will build that habit.

479
00:24:41.050 --> 00:24:43.220
And habits are automatic, right?

480
00:24:43.240 --> 00:24:45.090
And when you have an automatic habit.

481
00:24:45.120 --> 00:24:49.900
It's very easy to go from 15 to 20,
from 20 to 30 minutes a day.

482
00:24:49.920 --> 00:24:53.050
That difference doesn't feel like
much when it's already a habit.

483
00:24:53.080 --> 00:24:55.420
So consistency over intensity.
Okay?

484
00:24:55.450 --> 00:24:58.460
Remember, 3 hours one day per week is way

485
